Usage info:
tomovee_miner [option] <path>

Options:
 -s, --storage <st>  This storage is called <st>.
 -m, --mtime         Use modification time to indicate when was the file added.
 -d, --delete        Delete from database paths no longer found in this run.
 -D, --delete-all    Delete from database paths no longer found in this run
                     and files without any path.
 -i, --include       Include only following directories (path relative to the root)
 -e, --exclude       Exclude following directories (path relative to the root)
 -v, --verbose       Be more verbose.
 -h, --help          Show this help.

